            "title": "美檢控四人走私 向華供英偉達晶片",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美檢控四人走私 向華供英偉達晶片\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/oJEJ6NBF5dDMSFRCxlBfag--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-05/41d8dee0-3801-11f0-b2fb-cdd411b2eee1\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美檢控四人走私 向華供英偉達晶片</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
